---
title: Grilled Apricot-Mustard Salmon Dinner with Wild Rice and Summery Veggies
description: Get ready for bright summer flavours to take centre stage in tonight's dinner. Crisp baby cucumbers, sweet stone fruit and snappy asparagus are some of season's best offerings, and they're all part of this delicious grilled dish.
